sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor MG as Manager
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Promotion as Promotion Service
    participant PromotionDB as Promotion DB - MongoDB

    MG->>GW: POST /api/promotions
    Note over MG,GW: promotionName, benefitType<br/>startDate, endDate<br/>couponCode tuy chon, maxUsage tuy chon
    GW->>Promotion: Forward request - yeu cau auth MANAGER

    alt Thieu promotionName hoac benefitType
        Promotion-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>MG: Ten chuong trinh va loai uu dai la bat buoc
    else Thieu startDate hoac endDate
        Promotion-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>MG: Ngay bat dau va ket thuc la bat buoc
    else startDate la ngay trong qua khu
        Promotion-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>MG: Ngay bat dau khong duoc la ngay trong qua khu
    else endDate truoc startDate
        Promotion-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>MG: Ngay ket thuc phai sau hoac bang ngay bat dau
    else couponCode bi trung
        Promotion->>PromotionDB: promotion.findByCouponCode(couponCode)
        PromotionDB-->>Promotion: promotion da ton tai
        Promotion-->>GW: 409 Conflict
        GW-->>MG: Ma coupon nay da duoc su dung
    else Hop le
        Promotion->>PromotionDB: promotion.findAll - dem de sinh promotionId
        PromotionDB-->>Promotion: danh sach promotionId hien co
        Promotion->>Promotion: generateNextPromotionId - PROMO_001, PROMO_002...

        Promotion->>Promotion: computeStatus - tinh trang thai tu ngay
        Note over Promotion: startDate > hom nay -> PLANNED<br/>endDate < hom nay -> EXPIRED<br/>con lai -> ACTIVE

        Promotion->>PromotionDB: promotion.create
        Note over Promotion,PromotionDB: promotionId, promotionName, benefitType<br/>couponCode normalized UPPERCASE<br/>usageCount=0, status, createdBy
        PromotionDB-->>Promotion: promotion record

        Promotion->>PromotionDB: promotionCondition.createOrUpdate
        Note over Promotion,PromotionDB: Tao condition rong gan voi promotionId<br/>triggerProducts, rewardProducts se cap nhat sau

        Promotion-->>GW: 201 Created
        Note over Promotion,GW: promotionId, promotionName<br/>benefitType, status, couponCode
        GW-->>MG: Tao chuong trinh khuyen mai thanh cong
    end

    Note over MG,PromotionDB: Buoc tiep theo - cap nhat dieu kien<br/>PUT /api/promotions/:id/conditions<br/>triggerProducts, rewardProducts, minimumOrderAmount
